				<p><p>It seems like you are asking how to do the line following, so here's one way to think about it:</p>

<p>Once you have found the line, one way to follow it is to follow one of the edges of the line. For example: following the right edge could be done like this: </p>

<p>If you have two color sensors (left and right) and the left sensor is on the line while the right is not, continue forward.</p>

<p>If the right sensor or both sensors detect the line, turn right slightly until the robot is back on the right edge. </p>

<p>If the left sensor doesn't detect the line and the right doesn't detect the line, the robot has gone off the right side of the line. Turn left.</p>
